        <div class="px-5 pb-5 text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Copilot is built into Windows 11, Edge, and Microsoft 365. Microsoft reports hundreds of millions of Copilot interactions monthly, many from users who access it passively through Microsoft products rather than by actively seeking out an AI tool. This passive distribution is what makes Copilot unique. Users encounter it through their existing workflow, not by choosing to visit a separate AI platform.</div>
